y runs and lower crude output, sources say #oott https://t.co/1P9wcidzmd", "time": "13:19", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119640, "views": 8436, "likes": 24, "replies": 0, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2064004710877556992", "url": "https://x.com/OilandEnergy/status/2064004710877556903", "text": "Oil markets may be underestimating the risks of a prolonged U.S./Israel-Iran stalemate. With the Strait of Hormuz effectively closed and global inventories drawing fast, analysts warn Brent could break above $120-$135/bbl later this summer. #Oil #OOTT #EnergyMarkets \n\nhttps://t.co/eD2sQ8JgSV", "time": "15:20", "author": "OilandEnergy", "author_name": "OilPrice.com", "followers": 95942, "views": 6916, "likes": 95, "replies": 4, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 11, "labels": null}, {"id": "2064029203318619904", "url": "https://x.com/OilandEnergy/status/2064029203318620517", "text": "The oil market may be far closer to a supply crunch than prices suggest. Analysts warn global inventories are rapidly approaching “operational stress” levels as the Strait of Hormuz disruption continues to drain critical buffer stocks. #Oil #EnergySecurity #OOTT \n\nhttps://t.co/yX1meM9df4", "time": "16:58", "author": "OilandEnergy", "author_name": "OilPrice.com", "followers": 95942, "views": 76464, "likes": 362, "replies": 25, "retweets": 103, "quotes": 9, "bookmarks": 55, "labels": null}, {"id": "2064035077374332928", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2064035077374332977", "text": "US SPR crude inventories fell by ~7.9mb w/w to 349.2mb last week #oott     \nSour down ~4.1mb to 216.0mb   \nSweet down ~3.8mb to 133.2mb https://t.co/raJ3rv6weK", "time": "17:21", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119640, "views": 68726, "likes": 223, "replies": 14, "retweets": 42, "quotes": 9, "bookmarks": 25, "labels": null}, {"id": "2064042489200132096", "url": "https://x.com/NuggetCapital/status/2064042489200132282", "text": "POLL: 3 months of Hormuz Strait closure and oil is fighting from the left corner to hold $90. What will the price of WTI be after the Hormuz Strait \"re-opens\" after 3- months? #OOTT #hormuzStrait $CL $BZ #crudeoil #nuggetcapitalpartners #rogerlafontaine", "time": "17:50", "author": "NuggetCapital", "author_name": "Nugget Capital Partners (NCP)", "followers": 7486, "views": 3456, "likes": 4, "replies": 14, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2064044809820732928", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2064044809820733490", "text": "European LNG imports fell in May as Qatari cargoes disappeared from the market and US deliveries dropped sharply, but stronger exports from Algeria and Russia helped cushion the impact and limit the overall decline. @Kpler #OOTT #LNG", "time": "18:00", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 173868, "views": 15142, "likes": 69, "replies": 4, "retweets": 13, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2064057126134153984", "url": "https://x.com/pickeringenergy/status/2064057126134153723", "text": "A 20-minute walk around energy markets with IBD's Alexis Garcia. We hit market complacency, 2+ months to stabilize inventories after peace evenutally arrives, US industry activity trends, Majors vs. Independent E&amp;Ps..a good conversation #EFT #OOTT \n\nhttps://t.co/FSuXl7gv22", "time": "18:49", "author": "pickeringenergy", "author_name": "Dan Pickering", "followers": 36195, "views": 3353, "likes": 19, "replies": 1, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 9, "labels": null}, {"id": "2064122646267145984", "url": "https://x.com/SamanthaLaDuc/status/2064122646267146278", "text": "Stealing/Seizing Kharg Island is still the plan!\n\nEvery stupid deflection headline between Trump &amp; Netanyahu’s bromance brawl is pure bullocks. \n\nWatch what they do not what they say! #OOTT", "time": "23:09", "author": "SamanthaLaDuc", "author_nam